  "price_level": 2,
  "rating": 4.3,
  "reviews": [
    {
      "author_name": "Berele",
      "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/117663769568780389806/reviews",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "en",
      "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX-rYfcQui2PgTOhi3PVgUFmPf_soawpysFZ4-C5Oe5gyiQYZUzlw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6",
      "rating": 3,
      "relative_time_description": "2 months ago",
      "text": "A charming old-style Italian restaurant with a nice atmosphere but uneven execution. The cappuccino was excellent, rich and perfectly made, easily the highlight of the meal. The rest of the food was just fine. The bread didn\u2019t seem fresh, though the olive oil was high quality. The beef was tender but overly salty, which made it hard to enjoy.\n\nThe service felt detached. Our waiter seemed in a hurry and never quite connected with us, though he became much friendlier when it was time for the check. The place itself has a lot of character with its brick walls, framed photos, and cozy layout, but small details held the experience back.\n\nIt\u2019s not a bad spot, just one that could be great with a little more care in both the food and the service.",
      "time": 1762096968,
      "translated": false
    },
    {
      "author_name": "Anu P",
      "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110483692548178046045/reviews",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "en",
      "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUkFTdwm-Fd3DFTD5qi0MZbwEn7zKiXsOuo2w7foJwtbFzvg1t_=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2",
      "rating": 5,
      "relative_time_description": "5 months ago",
      "text": "We had lunch at this cozy restaurant. Our waiter Amar was great and he replaced meat with eggplant for my panini order when i told him i want a vegetarian option. We also\nordered a Cesar salad and Scampi oreganata and everything was delicious!!",
      "time": 1755472157,
      "translated": false
    },
    {
      "author_name": "Darwin Jimenez",
      "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112418105484941786801/reviews",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "en",
      "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWkDmUHHUFLCC4cqAy8OoZLmcn7vxsqb8j03UWBMu8Zm4LWd06b=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo",
      "rating": 5,
      "relative_time_description": "2 months ago",
      "text": "My family and I entered after the 2025 New York City Marathon. Even though it was a busy night, we waited about 15 minutes. The waiter gave me a great suggestion that was perfect. My photo isn't very good because I shared my dish with my sister, but everything was delicious. I ordered the pasta the waiter recommended, and my sister had that tasty lasagna.",
      "time": 1762305622,
      "translated": false
    },
    {
      "author_name": "CallmeZ",
      "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/117843534703716404787/reviews",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "en",
      "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU3SsUeM1g9OGHHrbfmL1wdDnxwspokpT7fca4Ek4RkbMK3RvdFFQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3",
      "rating": 5,
      "relative_time_description": "3 weeks ago",
      "text": "Came in for lunch with my mother and had a wonderful time. The inside is cozy, like you\u2019re in an Italian grandma\u2019s living room. The music was aromatic and set the mood beautifully. The food was absolutely delicious, I had the prefix lunch deal ($35) that came with a glass of wine, an appetizer and an entree. i got the John Dory fish which is amazing. Me and my mother sat on the side at a two person table where we were able to watch the people and the street. It was beautiful. Would definitely come back and recommend others to come here.",
      "time": 1766782429,
      "translated": false
    },
    {
      "author_name": "Marta Galmozzi",
      "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101802180343156451774/reviews",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "en",
      "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUMbNLl87UdiFKtaIPzHONlCsqfVeOHjaSQcOICFaj_Rzs0sEiJYQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5",
      "rating": 3,
      "relative_time_description": "a month ago",
      "text": "We ordered bucatini all\u2019amatriciana and fettuccine bolognese. As an Italian, I can say this is not an authentic Italian restaurant. The quality of the food was low and it was hard to digest for hours afterward. The service was kind, and the place is cozy.",
      "time": 1765897336,
      "translated": false
    }
  ],
